# Part 3h-followup — fourth-pair scan (sub-typing stays held)
#
# After PR #2027 landed Pair 27 (lc-energy ↔ lc-attunement) and named
# sub-typing actionable at the next attestation matching one of the six
# substrate-flavors (value / voltage / nutrients / perception /
# metabolic-energy / harmonic-resonance), a fourth-pair scan walked
# the 100%-covered concept corpus for the activating attestation.
#
# Verdict: no clean fourth pair on careful reading. Sub-typing stays
# held; the kind remains 3 pairs / 6 substrate-flavors.
#
# Candidates examined (recorded so a future walk inherits the
# discernment — these decisions are not re-litigation territory; they
# are the body's current settled reading):
#
# - lc-circulation (web/circulating, value-primary) — load-bearing
#   carrier of the kind teaching. Already source-flow-paired with
#   lc-offering (Pair 15). PR #2025's "same medium as seed" decline
#   still stands at 100% coverage: the medium is primarily value-
#   flow with mixed substance undertones, and the partner candidates
#   below all fail.
#
# - lc-network (web/circulating, inter-community substrate) — carries
#   "no central node, surplus flowing by gradient" load-bearingly.
#   A lc-circulation ↔ lc-network pair sits on the boundary between
#   three kinds: circulation-pattern, scale-paired (intra- vs inter-
#   community), and source-flow. Forcing it into circulation-pattern
#   would muddy the kind's seam from "different substrate of flow"
#   toward "different scale of same flow." Most cleanly reads as
#   scale-paired if the body later names it.
#
# - lc-resonating (web/RADIATING) — would carry sonic substrate as
#   harmonic-resonance's second instance, but body attests radiating
#   not circulating. Pair 24 (lc-resonating ↔ lc-sensing) already
#   pairs as source-flow with the load-bearing seam "resonating is
#   the radiating face; sensing is the receptive-circulating face."
#   The kind requires both poles to be circulations. Honest decline.
#
# - lc-w-coherence (web/RADIATING) — alignment teaching, not flow.
#   Fails both-circulations requirement.
#
# - lc-w-field (holographic-cell, not web) — fails form requirement.
#
# - lc-cross-connection (web/circulating) — different load-bearing
#   teaching: "the pull is the door" (oversoul-having-all-lives-at-
#   once-as-integration-mechanism). Not "no central command, every
#   cell senses gradients." Fails the kind's teaching.
#
# - lc-trust-as-gateway, lc-coherence-over-control (dyad-mirror),
#   lc-nervous-system (ennead) — fail form requirement.
#
# What this scan reveals: at 100% coverage, the *clean* circulation-
# pattern attestations have already found each other in the body.
# Remaining web/circulating cells that brush the kind's signature
# either carry a different teaching, are radiating-not-circulating
# (and so naturally pair as source-flow's emission/reception
# complement), or sit on a boundary with scale-paired. The body's
# discernment is doing exactly what it should: when the kind is
# honest, forcing a fourth pair to activate sub-typing would dilute
# the seam. The clean diversification (six flavors, zero repeats
# across three pairs) IS the structure.
#
# Sub-typing stays held until the body produces the second-instance-
# per-flavor naturally — either through a new concept grown into
# that shape, or through a future walk that reads an existing cell
# differently after further attestation has shifted the field.

