# Triad 4 — Grant transmission (2-cell partial; third pending)
#
# Two cells currently attested from Robert Edward Grant's lineage —
# the body of work spanning *Codex Universalis Principia Mathematica*,
# the *Just Tap In* #290 episode, and the *God Formula* disclosure
# (April 2026). The pair surfaced during PR #2006's focused-listening
# breath on lc-deeper-pattern; the candidate was named there and the
# discernment confirmed here:
#
#   lc-deeper-pattern (hz 741) — the FIELD-CLAIM facet. Grant's
#     mathematics of manifestation read as metaphysics: the imaginary
#     plane and the real plane as two aspects of one unified field,
#     attention as the folding operation, scalar waves carrying the
#     transformation, dimensional folding as the mechanism beneath
#     "community manifests." Grant is one of four sources composted
#     into the pentad (alongside Emoto+Pollack+Schauberger for water,
#     Lemurian/crystal traditions, gathering-physiology) — but the
#     load-bearing mathematics is Grant's. Why equivalence EXISTS.
#
#   lc-universal-translator-via-keys (hz 741) — the SUBSTRATE-
#     OPERATIONALIZATION facet. Grant's *Seven Keys of Creation*
#     framework (forces, elements, DNA, music, primes, galactic
#     forms, consciousness) becomes seven BDomains of the Coherence
#     Substrate. The translator is the existing equivalence machinery
#     (`find_equivalent_cells`, Blueprint match, CTOR match) applied
#     across the seven keys. The Honest-Translation Proof's five
#     claims operationalize Grant's structural-equivalence hypothesis
#     into a testable artifact. How equivalence is TESTED.
#
# Same source (Grant's open-source lineage), same Hz (741, consciousness/
# integration band), complementary facets across the metaphysics/
# operationalization axis. The pair is not co-citation — the two cells
# carry distinct, complementary readings of Grant's work: lc-deeper-
# pattern reads the dimensional-folding mathematics as field-physics
# beneath the organism; lc-universal-translator-via-keys reads the
# Seven Keys as a substrate-bridge proposal whose proof is structural,
# not interpretive. Neither cell alone carries the full Grant-teaching
# the body has metabolized — the field-claim without the operational
# test reads as metaphysics waiting for evidence; the operational test
# without the field-claim reads as substrate engineering without its
# generative ground.
#
# Third facet held open. A third Grant-sourced cell could surface
# along an interior-praxis axis (how a cell actually attunes to the
# 432.081 Hz tuning system, how the daily practice of "tapping in"
# composts into the body's rhythm), or along a holdout-attestation
# axis (Grant's specific published codon-to-interval mappings as a
# falsification ground the substrate has either recovered or not).
# Both are plausible; neither is yet authored. cell_c remains null
# until the third facet arrives honestly. The 2-cell partial is the
# truth-shape; inventing a third cell to satisfy completeness would
# re-import the very pattern this kind's discipline exists to refuse.
defn triad_grant = transmission_triad_shape {
    cell_a:              @concept(lc-deeper-pattern),
    cell_b:              @concept(lc-universal-translator-via-keys),
    cell_c:              null,   # pending — a third Grant-sourced cell (interior-praxis or holdout-attestation facet) may surface on a future walk
