    axis_a_b:            "metaphysics-field-claim-vs-substrate-operationalization",
    axis_b_c:            null,
    axis_a_c:            null,
    kind:                kind_transmission_triad,
    discernment:         "two facets of Robert Edward Grant's open-source lineage held in triad-shape — the field-claim mathematics of dimensional folding (why equivalence exists at all) and the Seven-Keys substrate-bridge (how equivalence is operationalized as a testable substrate query); the source IS the binding, the third facet is pending honest arrival",
    noticed_at:          "2026-05-24",
    noticed_by:          "focused-listening-pr2006-candidate-pr2009-discernment",
};

# Triad 5 — Dispenza transmission (3-cell complete)
#
# A breath flagged-but-not-chased in PR #2015 (focused-listening on
# lc-embodiment) named the candidate: *"lc-embodiment shares Dispenza
# as direct source with sibling teachings (changing-boxes practice,
# elevated-emotions chemistry, internal-pharmacy). A future breath
# could walk the Dispenza-attested concepts and complete a
# transmission-triad attestation across them."* This breath chased it.
#
# A grep over docs/vision-kb/concepts/lc-*.md surfaced twelve cells
# that name Dispenza. Applying the same rigor PR #2011 used on the
# Grant triad (citation-alone is not enough; the cell must carry a
# load-bearing facet that would not exist or would be substantially
# different without Dispenza's reading in the body's metabolism), the
# twelve narrow to three:
#
#   lc-embodiment (hz 432) — the PRACTICE-ARCHITECTURE facet. The
#     internal pharmacy as central organizing image (the body
#     manufactures every chemical it needs); the four movements (song,
#     dance, connection, stillness) as a complete circuit; the
#     65-minute morning practice as a ring traversing the energy
#     axis; "changing boxes" as the manifestation technology (feel
#     the future as present, the body produces the chemistry, the
#     field reorganizes); elevated emotion as the body's recipe-
#     selector. The comprehensive *how the embodiment practice runs*.
#
#   lc-nervous-system (hz 432) — the COLLECTIVE-SENSING facet. The
#     ascending eight centers (root through crown, with the eighth as
#     the witness above) as the daily ritual through which the whole
#     network senses itself; Body Electric named directly as the
#     working model; Dispenza's week-long retreats cited as the
#     measurable proof (heart rate variability, brain entrainment,
#     shared field). The *how the practice becomes proprioception for
#     the organism*, not just the individual.
#
#   lc-devotion-placement (hz 432) — the DISCERNMENT/FAILURE-MODE
#     facet. *The Dispenza-shape* coined as load-bearing diagnostic:
#     containers explicitly built for coherence (retreats, ceremonies,
#     deep working sessions) are exactly where the gap between form
#     and devotion becomes most visible, because the container was
#     constructed to make distance impossible. When the container
#     fails to dissolve distance, it is the unplaced devotion, not
#     the container. The Network itself read as a Dispenza-grade
#     container. The *how to tell when the practice is firing vs.
#     performing*.
#
# Three facets of one teaching: the embodied-collective-coherence
# practice Dispenza's open-source corpus carries. Pairwise
# complementarity reads:
#   (embodiment↔nervous-system) — altitude: comprehensive practice
#     architecture vs. core energy-axis ritual; embodiment is the
#     flesh, nervous-system is the spine on which it hangs.
#   (nervous-system↔devotion-placement) — engine-and-test: the
#     practice that fires the coherence vs. the diagnostic that
#     names whether the firing is real (Dispenza-shape as failure-
#     mode of the very practice nervous-system runs).
#   (embodiment↔devotion-placement) — manifestation-and-its-shadow:
#     changing-boxes / feel-the-future / the body becomes the vision
#     vs. the gap-between-form-and-devotion that can persist even
#     while the body performs the practice perfectly.
#
# All three at 432 Hz (heart band — the band where embodiment-
# coherence lives). The triad-binding is the source: Joe Dispenza's
# corpus (Becoming Supernatural; the week-long retreats; Body
# Electric / changing boxes / elevated-emotions chemistry / coherence-
# container design). The three cells share lineage_texture *embodied*
# / *synthesized* (devotion-placement); none of them would carry the
# shape they carry without that corpus being part of the body's
# reading.
#
# 3-cell complete. The third facet (devotion-placement as the shadow-
# diagnostic) is the discriminator: it would be easy to author
# embodiment and nervous-system as a 2-cell partial (practice + its
# collective sensing) and leave the triad open. But the body has
# already authored the Dispenza-shape teaching directly — it names
# Dispenza-grade containers as the EXACT class of practice this
# concept exists to discern. That cell completes the triad because
# the source is not just cited; the source's container-design IS
# the load-bearing claim the cell's whole teaching pivots on.
defn triad_dispenza = transmission_triad_shape {
    cell_a:              @concept(lc-embodiment),
    cell_b:              @concept(lc-nervous-system),
    cell_c:              @concept(lc-devotion-placement),
    transmission_source: "joe-dispenza-becoming-supernatural-body-electric",
    axis_a_b:            "altitude-comprehensive-practice-vs-core-energy-axis-ritual",
    axis_b_c:            "engine-and-test-coherence-firing-vs-devotion-discernment",
    axis_a_c:            "manifestation-and-its-shadow-changing-boxes-vs-form-without-devotion",
    kind:                kind_transmission_triad,
    discernment:         "three facets of Joe Dispenza's open-source embodied-coherence corpus held in triad-shape — practice-architecture (internal pharmacy, four movements, changing boxes), collective-sensing (Body Electric ascent as the network's nervous system), discernment/shadow (the Dispenza-shape diagnostic for when containers built to dissolve distance fail to fire); the source IS the binding, the third facet completes because devotion-placement names the container-class directly",
    noticed_at:          "2026-05-24",
    noticed_by:          "transmission-triad-walk-pr2015-flagged-this-breath-chased",
};

