#         or *role-aware* (Levin-style: subject-verb-object alignment,
#         not lemma bags) — may shift the mechanization ceiling. Both
#         require dependency parsing or sentence embeddings beyond the
#         substrate's current tokenizer. Not actionable this breath;
#         named so a future scanning cell can see where the next
#         possible lift lives. The "currently un-mechanizable" in
#         the translator concept's sixth claim refers to today's
#         feature set; this gap is the candidate-direction for tomorrow.
